body:
This is a follow up to #14015 and #13798 .

All commits are rebased to the CMSSW_8_1_CLANG_X_2016-04-24-0000 IB such that #13987 lies below, with fixes to make things actually work.

Some points mentioned in #14015 are still relevant, but everything that I got feedback to is fixed.

@makortel regarding the Certification module, I now remove that in DQMOffline_CRT_cff.py, even though I still don't get how that finds its way into the offline config (cert-stuff is removed in SiPixelOfflineDQM). And, said module crashes due to code like this `float dcsFrac = (iGetter.get("Pixel/EventInfo/DCSSummary"))->getFloatValue();`, though I can't see immediatly which histogram is missing due to my changes (probably all...).

@slava77 I now make the TrackerTopology internal structs visible to the outside. I am not sure whether that is a good idea, but I agree it is better than what we had before.

@smuzaffar there are now 3 new packages, one with shared code and two that use this code for digis and clusters. More packages will come in the future, but I can't tell yet how we will call them.
UPDATE: now 4. Two for shared code and config, two for the plugins.

Overall, I think this is in a mergeable shape now. Let me know if you think different. Also, chasing IBs and rebasing ~100 commits each time starts to get annoying.
